stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle

    Idle --> SolarCharging : T_coll > T_tank_btm + 7°C
    Idle --> GreenhouseHeating : T_greenhouse < 10°C
    Idle --> ActiveDrain : T_outdoor < 2°C\nAND collectors filled
    Idle --> Emergency : T_greenhouse < 5°C\nAND tank insufficient

    SolarCharging --> Idle : T_coll < T_tank_btm + 3°C
    SolarCharging --> ActiveDrain : T_outdoor < 2°C

    GreenhouseHeating --> Idle : T_greenhouse ≥ 12°C
    GreenhouseHeating --> Emergency : T_greenhouse < 5°C\nAND tank insufficient

    ActiveDrain --> CollectorsDrained : flow sensor = 0
    CollectorsDrained --> Idle : waiting
    CollectorsDrained --> Refill : T_outdoor > 5°C\nAND sun available

    Refill --> SolarCharging : collectors filled

    Emergency --> Idle : T_greenhouse ≥ 10°C

    note right of SolarCharging
        VI-btm OPEN, VO-coll OPEN, V_ret OPEN
        Pump ON, Fan OFF
    end note

    note right of GreenhouseHeating
        VI-top OPEN, VO-rad OPEN
        Pump ON, Fan ON
    end note

    note right of ActiveDrain
        VI-coll OPEN, VO-tank OPEN, V_air OPEN
        Pump ON until flow=0
    end note

    note right of Emergency
        All valves CLOSED
        Space heater ON (2kW)
        Jäspi element ON (optional)
    end note
